column2: select s.specobjid, s.z, SL.ew as EW_Ha, p.objid, p.petromag_u, p.petromag_g, p.petromag_r, p.petromag_i, p.petromag_z from photoprimary p   join specobj s   on p.objid = s.bestobjid   join SpecLine SL   on s.specobjid = SL.specobjid WHERE   s.z > #   and   petroR5#_r > #   and   petroR5#_g > #   and   (p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g - #*log1#(#*s.z)) > (#*(p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g - p.petroMag_r - p.extinction_r) - #)   and   (p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g + #*log1#(p.petroR5#_g) - p.petroMag_r - p.extinction_r - #*log1#(p.petroR5#_r)) <= #   and   (# + p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g + #*log1#(p.petroR5#_g)) < (# - #*(p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g - p.petroMag_r + p.extinction_r + #*log1#(p.petroR5#_g) - #*log1#(p.petroR5#_r)))   and   SL.lineID = #   and   SL.ew > #)   as f   JOIN   SpecLine SL   ON   f.specobjid = SL.specobjid WHERE   SL.lineID = #   and   log1#(SL.ew/f.EW_Ha) < #
